<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, December 24 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 2,492.55 on Thursday, up
90.66 points, or 3.76 percent, from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover stood at over 47 trillion Turkish Liras (152
million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index rose 123.23 points, or 4.01 percent, to
close at 3,154.19 points, the industrial index climbed 54.64
points, or 3.01 percent, to close at 1,855.10 points and the
services index increased 108.39 points, or 3.37 percent, to close
at 3,488.35 points. 
