memoranda with Fokion Fotiadis, the head of the European
Commission's delegation to Bucharest.
</P>
<P>
Under the three memoranda, Romania becomes recipient of 50
million ECU, to reconstruct the areas hit by mines restructuring
and floods in 1998, upgrade the infrastructure and restructure the
finances.
</P>
<P>
