<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 25 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major
world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on December 26 issued by
China's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. -5 degrees C., max. 7 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 5 degrees C., max. 12 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 24 degrees C., max. 33 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Sydney: min. 18 degrees C., max. 26 degrees C., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Karachi: min. 16 degrees C., max. 28 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Cairo: min. 11 degrees C., max. 19 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Moscow: min. -11 degrees C., max. -5 degrees C., overcast, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt: min. -2 degrees C., max. 2 degrees C., overcast,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Paris: min. 3 degrees C., max. 7 degrees C., drizzle, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
London: min. 4 degrees C., max. 8 degrees C., drizzle, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
