husband Xu Xiaoping, include many precious shots which recorded
the great men's working and life experience. They are well
received by students and teachers in Qinghua University, where the
exhibition was held.
</P>
<P>
Hou worked in Zhongnanhai, the seat of Chinese Communist Party
Central Committee headquarters and the State Council, as a special
photographer for Mao Zedong and other central government leaders
for a dozen years. She took more than 10,000 pictures during the
period.
</P>
<P>
