funding for railway construction in southwest China will be
substantially increased next year, with funding for the
Zhuzhou-Liupanshui and Neijiang-Kunming railways expected to
double.
</P>
<P>
Over 30 percent of the substantial funding in railway
construction designed to stimulate domestic demand has been
earmarked for the southwest. 
