<HEADLINE> Overseas Investment Spurs Guangzhou's Commercial Sector </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, December 25 (Xinhua) -- Overseas-funded commercial
enterprises in the southern city of Guangzhou reported a total
retail sales of 4.82 billion yuan in the first 10 months this
year, up 18.8 percent from the same year-earlier period.
