<HEADLINE> Dortmund Goalkeeper Klos Joins Rangers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, December 24 (Xinhua) -- Rangers Thursday signed
Germany's Borussia Dortmund goalkeeper Stefan Klos in a 700,000
pounds (about 1.17 million U.S. dollars) deal, according to
reports from Glasgow.
</P>
<P>
