<HEADLINE> Universidad Catolica Qualifies for Libertadores Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTIAGO, December 24 (Xinhua) -- Universidad Catolica of
Chile qualified for next year's South American Libertadores Cup
soccer tournament by defeating Universidad de Chile 4-2 on
penalties.
</P>
<P>
The final of the four-team playoff ended level on aggregate
after a 0-0 draw on Wednesday, sending the tie into a shootout.
</P>
